    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，FabLab成员或访客通过镜面交互。那这个系统边界内部应该包含哪些核心组件？我看到有UI层、业务逻辑层这些？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SmartMirror System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，系统内部我规划了四个部分：前端是MagicMirror UI，后端是Spring Boot做的核心服务，还有一个独立的AI后端专门做人脸识别和聊天，数据库用PostgreSQL加上pgvector扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MagicMirror UI",
        "Spring Boot Backend",
        "AI Backend",
        "PostgreSQL + pgvector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以系统边界内是这四块。我注意到AI后端和数据库是分开的，AI那边需要向量检索能力对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI Backend",
        "PostgreSQL + pgvector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，人脸特征要存成向量，聊天上下文也可能要用向量检索。pgvector就是干这个的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI Backend",
        "PostgreSQL + pgvector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那外部依赖呢？AI后端要调LLM吧，是本地部署还是云服务？",
